Library Guidelines
The Engineer Accelerator
Malcolm Knapp

Symbols
	- Origin is center of the symbol
	- ICs
		- Follow Electrical logic not physical layout
			- VCC upper left
			- GND lower right
			- Inputs on left
			- Outputs on right
	- Name and Value Called out

Footprint
	- Name called out
	- Must have a component outline 
	- Origin in the center of the footprint
	- ICs
		- Call out pin 1
	- Connectors
		- Call out pin 1
	- Diodes 
		- Call out polarity
	- Capacitors
		- For polarized capacitors call out positive pin

		


	
